# Deprecated — use `.cursor/rules/rules/template.mdc`

**Mandatory template for new rule files:** **`.cursor/rules/rules/template.mdc`**

Copy that file to **`.cursor/rules/<name>/<name>.mdc`** (or a grouped subfolder like **`infras/`**) per **`.cursor/rules/rules/rules.mdc`**.

The older **`.cursor/templates/rules-file-template.md`** is retired — do not use for new rule files.
